description: Get more veg into your day with this easy zucchini muffin recipe. Nutritionally approved, these tasty muffins are the perfect snack for on the go.
name: Easy Cheesy Zucchini Muffins Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 4.5 cups Macro Organic wholemeal spelt flour

recipeInstructions.text: Divide mixture among cases. Top with extra zucchini and season with pepper, then bake for 30 minutes or until golden and a skewer inserted into centres comes out clean.
